com.bdl.auto.impl

Annotation Type AutoImpl


  • @Retention(value=CLASS)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface AutoImpl
    Indicates that a class should have a concrete implementation class generated for it.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      ImplOption booleanImpl
      The implementation to use for methods that return a boolean.
      ImplOption numericImpl
      The implementation to use for methods that return a numeric type.
      ImplOption objectImpl
      The implementation to use for methods that return a non-String, non-boxed Object type.
      ImplOption stringImpl
      The implementation to use for methods that return a String.
      ImplOption value
      The default implementation to use when implementing methods.
      ImplOption voidImpl
      The implementation to use for methods that do not return a value.

    • Element Detail

        public abstract ImplOption value
        The default implementation to use when implementing methods.

        Cannot be ImplOption.USE_PARENT.

        Default:
